raw_text = "~ start
## 6pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Mabel: Class is DONE 🙌
Mabel: I actually understood most of it today, go Mabel! 🤓
Player: Hey Mabes 😊
do Story.set_location(\"college_square_gardens\")
Mabel: Hi babes, just going home now
Mabel: It's not even fully dark out yet!! 😲
Mabel: I got out at a normal time yippee
Mabel: I can scurry like a brave chipmunk
Mabel: img: mabel/198
Player: Scurry? Haha
Mabel: SCURRY!
Mabel: This is basically prime scurrying conditions 😌
Mabel: Okay scurrying home NOW, full chipmunk mode engaged 🐿️💨 *Zoom*
do advance_time(1, 0)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Phew!! Home, showered, and FINALLY reunited with my bed! 😮‍💨
Player: Welcome back!
Mabel: Thaaanks
Mabel: PinkThought: That guy wasn't-..
Mabel: Thought: Nope!! We do not finish that thought
Mabel: Anywayyy what's my favorite boy been up to today 🥰
- Just thinking about you
	Player: Just thinking about you
	Mabel: STOPP 🥺
	Mabel: You can't just SAY stuff like that omg
	Mabel: PinkThought: Now my whole face is warm, jeez
- Homework is killing me
	Player: Homework is killing me
	Mabel: Nooo not my poor babe 😭
	Mabel: Want me to tutor you privately? Hehe, I'm not cheap!
	Player: 😆
Mabel: Ooh and it's SO peaceful in here tonight
Mabel: Not a single peep from next door for once 😌
Mabel: I might get real human sleep, wild concept I know
Player: Get some rest then, you earned it
Mabel: I'm gonna sleep so good tonight hehe
Mabel: sfx1: none: *knock knock*
Mabel: sfx: highmoan3: Eep!!
do heart(1)
Mabel: Thought: W-was that a KNOCK?? On MY door??
Mabel: Thought: That's never happened before..
Mabel: Hold on babe!! Someone's at my door 😨
Mabel: What should I do!?
- Answer it, duh!
	Player: Answer it, duh!
	Mabel: Can I just
- Pretend you aren't home
	Player: Pretend you aren't home
	Mabel: Great idea
Mabel: sfx1: none: *knock knock knock*
do heart(2)
Mabel: Gaaah, he's still here
Mabel: Okay 1 sec
Player: Tyt
do heart(1)
do echo_set([\"199\"])
Mabel: sfx: none: U-uhm... who is it...?
Mabel: Thought: Oh. OH. It's the guy from next door
Mabel: Thought: The... noisy one. We've literally never even talked
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh... hello! Is everything okay?
Mabel: sfx: none: Was I being too loud?
Mabel: Thought: Wait why would I be loud, HE'S the loud one
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh noticed me..? When I got home?
Mabel: Thought: He's all... smiley. Okay this is fine. Just be polite Mabel.
Mabel: sfx: none: Hang out??
Mabel: sfx: none: I don't know.. isn't it kind of late for that with classes and all that stuff
Mabel: sfx: none: That's super sweet but I'm pretty tired tonight
Mabel: sfx: none: \"Netflix and chill\"? Ohh you have Netflix?
Mabel: Thought: Spy Family on a bigger screen sounds like fun!
Mabel: Thought: Is that what he's doing late at night?
Mabel: sfx: none: That sounds nice but I have too much work to do, sorry..
Mabel: Thought: Is he... leaning on the doorframe?
Mabel: PinkThought: Why's he standing so close
Mabel: sfx: none: I really gotta sleep, but thanks for stopping by!
Mabel: sfx: none: Uhm.. sure... Another time sounds okay I guess
Mabel: Thought: MABEL YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR MIND!!
Player: You there?
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Yess I'm here!!! Sowwy!
Player: Who was it babe?
Mabel: Just the neighbor y'know... s-small talk!
Player: Oh what did she say?
Mabel: Thought: She? Oh he thinks it's a girl.. Uhm...
Mabel: She didn't say much 😅
Mabel: Thought: I have to avoid my neighbor too now hnghhh!!
Mabel: Anywaaay!
do heart(0)
Mabel: She uhm... invited me over to hang out and watch a movie or something
Mabel: I said not now but I thought it was nice 😊
Mabel: Told her maybe another time, I'm way too tired
Player: Probably for the best, you're catching up on your sleep!
Mabel: Yeah! That and plus I'd way rather be talking to youuu 🥰
Player: Same
Mabel: Thought: ...funny though
Mabel: PinkThought: It's been dead silent next door all night
Mabel: Thought: ...cause he's alone today right?
Mabel: Thought: But wait.. would I...
Mabel: PinkThought: Be making those noises-..
Mabel: Thought: Huh. WEIRD! Anyway!!
Mabel: Thought: I really wanna focus on babe
Mabel: Okay, no more distractions!! 😤
Mabel: Talking to you is a million times nicer anyway 🥰
Mabel: I'm so yawny, I could just pass out in your arms hehe
Mabel: You're honestly the comfiest part of my whole day babe, didja know that 😚
- Right back at you 🥰
	Player: Right back at you Mabes 🥰
	Player: You're the comfiest part of mine too
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: BABE that's toootally not FAIR 🥺
	Mabel: How am I supposed to sleep now with my heart all fluttery
	Mabel: PinkThought: He always knows exactly what to say ❤️
	Mabel: I'm not grinning in my pillow like a total dork 😳 Honest!
	Mabel: img: mabel/200
	Mabel: Okay maybe just a little hehe ☺️
	Player: 😍
	Player: That's not your usual PJs though
	Mabel: Ehm... yeah... 😅
	Mabel: This is part of a Sorority assimilation thing apparently
	Mabel: \"All Sorority girls must be dressed like a true Sorority girl\"
	Mabel: Something silly like that 😆
	- Is it comfortable?
		Player: Is it comfortable?
		Mabel: Not really... I prefer my PJs
		do heart(1)
		Mabel: These are a bit tight
		Mabel: PinkThought: They also sorta squeeze my crotch area
		Mabel: But I guess I have to haha
	- Do you like wearing it?
		Player: Do you like wearing it?
		do heart(1)
		Mabel: It's a bit more... revealing than I'd like haha..
		Mabel: Yeah I don't really know how I'd feel if someone other than you were to see me like this 😅
		Mabel: PinkThought: I think... I look good like this
	Mabel: PinkThought: I wonder how babe's hands would feel on my butt hehe
- You need the sleep
	Player: Sounds like you need the sleep
	Mabel: Yeah yeah, I know I know 🥱
	Mabel: Fiiine, you win. Bedtime it is 😌
do heart(0)
Mabel: Okayyy passing out for real this time
Mabel: Night night babe
Player: Night Mabes
Mabel: 🩷
=> END
"
